但是你可以来这里找 https://freshcoal.com/maincollection.php

获取用 1.13+ /give @p minecraft:player_head{SkullOwner:"名字"}

1.12 /give @p minecraft:skull 1 3 {SkullOwner:"名字"}

保证有联网，然后如果你游戏是1.13+的话输入以下指令：
/give @p player_head{display:{Name:"Glass of Beer"},SkullOwner:{Id:"e3e6b7a8-4246-41c4-9663-eddc9eda2eab",Properties:{textures:[{Value:"eyJ0ZXh0dXJlcyI6eyJTS0lOIjp7InVybCI6Imh0dHA6Ly90ZXh0dXJlcy5taW5lY3JhZnQubmV0L3RleHR1cmUvNDA1M2UyNjg2N2JiNTc1MzhlOTc4OTEzN2RiYmI1Mzc3NGUxOGVkYTZmZWY1MWNiMmVkZjQyNmIzNzI2NCJ9fX0="}]}}}
1.12和以下的话输入
/give @p skull 1 3 {display:{Name:"Glass of Beer"},SkullOwner:{Id:"e3e6b7a8-4246-41c4-9663-eddc9eda2eab",Properties:{textures:[{Value:"eyJ0ZXh0dXJlcyI6eyJTS0lOIjp7InVybCI6Imh0dHA6Ly90ZXh0dXJlcy5taW5lY3JhZnQubmV0L3RleHR1cmUvNDA1M2UyNjg2N2JiNTc1MzhlOTc4OTEzN2RiYmI1Mzc3NGUxOGVkYTZmZWY1MWNiMmVkZjQyNmIzNzI2NCJ9fX0="}]}}}
就能得到这样一个头

大概就是一杯啤酒吧
